  "title": {
    "en": "Table 4.3: Details of ex-gratia payments made to BOC workers during Covid-19 (tranche-wise)"
  },
  "summary": {
    "en": "Tranche-wise details of ex-gratia payments made to BOC workers in Delhi during Covid-19 across four instalments from March 2020 to July 2022. Against 10.52 lakh approved beneficiaries, only 9.48 lakh were actually paid, with total disbursement of ₹ 528.42 crore. Payments were spread over long periods in each tranche, reducing effectiveness as immediate relief."
  },
